## Safe to Modify
✅ /src/**/*.tsx (React components)
✅ /src/**/*.ts (TypeScript utilities/hooks)
✅ /api/**/*.ts (API endpoints)
✅ README.md (documentation)
✅ .claude/**/*.md (these instructions)

## When Adding Dependencies
1. Use exact versions: `npm install package@1.2.3`
2. Test thoroughly before committing
3. Update package.json manually if needed
4. Document in README if it's a major addition

## Protected Patterns
DO NOT change these established patterns:
- Arrow function parentheses: `(param) =>`
- Object brace spacing: `{name, value}`
- Tailwind-only styling (no custom CSS)
- Functional components only (no class components)
- TypeScript strict typing (all interfaces required)
